<p>However, challenges in DAO governance must be addressed to ensure effective and efficient operations.</p>



<p>One hypothetical example is a DAO that successfully coordinates global efforts to tackle climate change, bringing together individuals, organizations, and governments from around the world to work towards a common goal. This showcases the transformative power of Ethereum DAOs in facilitating global collaboration and impact.</p>
